title: Mehboob Shah wins NA-7 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Mehboob Shah has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-7 Lower Dir-II securing 84,843 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Jamaat e Islami candidate Muhammad Ismail, who bagged 31,133 votes.
The votersâ€™ turnout remained 42.66 percent.
